OL,7,FTwo men were convicted today of
OL,8,Fstirring up hatred by taking part in
OL,9,Fsinging an "abhorrent" song which
OL,10,Fmocked the murder of Michaela
OL,11,FMcAreavey.
OL,13,FSteven Kane, 26, received a four-month
OL,14,Fcustodial sentence, suspended for 18
OL,15,Fmonths, after pleading guilty to
OL,16,Finvolvement in the chanting inside an
OL,17,FOrange Order hall about the
OL,18,Fschoolteacher's death.
