OL,7,FCo-accused Dillion Kelly, 22, denied
OL,8,Fthe charge but was found guilty
OL,9,Ffollowing a contest at Belfast
OL,10,FMagistrates' Court. He will be
OL,11,Fsentenced next month.
OL,13,FMs McAreavey, the daughter of GAA
OL,14,Ffootball manager Mickey Harte, was
OL,15,Fattacked and killed by an intruder at
OL,16,Fher hotel room while on honeymoon in
OL,17,FMauritius in 2011.
OL,19,FIn May 2022 a number of people were
OL,20,Frecorded taking part in a song about
OL,21,Fher murder.
