OL,7,FThe video clip, live streamed from a
OL,8,Fhall in Dundonald, east Belfast during
OL,9,Fevents to celebrate the centenary of
OL,10,Fthe foundation of Northern Ireland,
OL,11,Fprovoked public outrage.
OL,13,FLast week a third defendant, 23-year-
OL,14,Fold Cian Jones, of Craigadick Road in
OL,15,FMaghera, was given 240 hours community
OL,16,Fservice after admitting behaviour
OL,17,Fintending to stir up hatred over his
OL,18,Fparticipation.
