OL,7,F"The song is undoubtedly mocking...
OL,8,Fbut the legislation is not designed to
OL,9,Fdeal with bad taste, even appallingly
OL,10,Fbad taste," he submitted.
OL,12,FHowever, District Judge George Conner
OL,13,Fruled that Kelly had joined in the
OL,14,Fsinging.
OL,16,F"I'm satisfied, having regard to all
OL,17,Fthe circumstances, that hatred was
OL,18,Flikely to be stirred up and there will
OL,19,Fbe a conviction," Mr Conner held.
