OL,7,FHe instructed Kelly to appear again in
OL,8,Fsix weeks time to be sentenced.
OL,10,FThe murder victim's widower, John
OL,11,FMcAreavey, provided a statement
OL,12,Fdescribing the distress caused him and
OL,13,Fthe wider family circle by the singing.
OL,15,FHe set out his belief that there was a
OL,16,Fhateful and hurtful intent behind it.
