OL,7,FKane's barrister told the court that
OL,8,Fhe was too young to have been aware of
OL,9,Fthe murder but "foolishly" decided to
OL,10,Fjoin in at an alcohol-fuelled
OL,11,Fenvironment.
OL,13,F"In that male company, being a young
OL,14,Fman trying to fit in, he went along
OL,15,F(with it)," counsel said.
OL,17,FMr Thompson added that Kane lost a
OL,18,Fwell-paid IT job and had to move home
OL,19,Fdue to threats after the footage was
OL,20,Fpublished.
